eu.diversify.trio.core

Class Dispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.diversify.trio.core.DefaultSystemVisitor
      • eu.diversify.trio.core.Dispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SystemVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Density, Statistics

    public class Dispatcher
extends DefaultSystemVisitor
    Dispatch visit events (i.e., enter, exit) to other visitors, to factor out the cost of traversing large models.
